lead_paragraph: Nomar Mazara hit a tiebreaking home run in the eighth inning and the Texas Rangers beat the Toronto Blue Jays 2-1 on Monday night for their fifth win in six games.

headline.print_headline: Mazara Hits Tiebreaking HR, Rangers Beat Blue Jays 2-1
